  "detailed_description": "\"In the aftermath of a global war between humans and machines, you are the only hope of destroying an A.I. keeping what's left of mankind enslaved in a virtual world called Veris\"<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/6220c024e0036541a4dbcfbd998e6f8f.poster.avif?t=1697834271\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/6220c024e0036541a4dbcfbd998e6f8f.webm?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/6220c024e0036541a4dbcfbd998e6f8f.mp4?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Veriscape is a 2D side-scroller/rhythm game where the stages are generated using music. Players will have to react fast as the music gets more intense<br><br>The main key to play the game is timing your jumps while keeping the pace, so that the multiverse death region won't catch you<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/55a803d2fe0219075f18685b8bc83695.poster.avif?t=1697834271\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/55a803d2fe0219075f18685b8bc83695.webm?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/55a803d2fe0219075f18685b8bc83695.mp4?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Controls Are Simple</h2><br>AD/Left and Right Arrow Keys to Move<br>Space bar to Jump/double Jump/triple Jump<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/12ef41e86a459b1f43452807829def65.poster.avif?t=1697834271\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/12ef41e86a459b1f43452807829def65.webm?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/12ef41e86a459b1f43452807829def65.mp4?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lore</h2><br>The idea behind this game started with a Game Jam about afterlife. It ended up not being submitted to that event, and it morphed into this awesomeness. I think it is a really fun game to play, and I hope you enjoy it as much as I did making it<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/0dd6ed96b7b4d5751207e40885ac9aec.poster.avif?t=1697834271\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/0dd6ed96b7b4d5751207e40885ac9aec.webm?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/0dd6ed96b7b4d5751207e40885ac9aec.mp4?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "\"In the aftermath of a global war between humans and machines, you are the only hope of destroying an A.I. keeping what's left of mankind enslaved in a virtual world called Veris\"<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/6220c024e0036541a4dbcfbd998e6f8f.poster.avif?t=1697834271\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/6220c024e0036541a4dbcfbd998e6f8f.webm?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/6220c024e0036541a4dbcfbd998e6f8f.mp4?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Veriscape is a 2D side-scroller/rhythm game where the stages are generated using music. Players will have to react fast as the music gets more intense<br><br>The main key to play the game is timing your jumps while keeping the pace, so that the multiverse death region won't catch you<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/55a803d2fe0219075f18685b8bc83695.poster.avif?t=1697834271\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/55a803d2fe0219075f18685b8bc83695.webm?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/55a803d2fe0219075f18685b8bc83695.mp4?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Controls Are Simple</h2><br>AD/Left and Right Arrow Keys to Move<br>Space bar to Jump/double Jump/triple Jump<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/12ef41e86a459b1f43452807829def65.poster.avif?t=1697834271\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/12ef41e86a459b1f43452807829def65.webm?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/12ef41e86a459b1f43452807829def65.mp4?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lore</h2><br>The idea behind this game started with a Game Jam about afterlife. It ended up not being submitted to that event, and it morphed into this awesomeness. I think it is a really fun game to play, and I hope you enjoy it as much as I did making it<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/0dd6ed96b7b4d5751207e40885ac9aec.poster.avif?t=1697834271\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/0dd6ed96b7b4d5751207e40885ac9aec.webm?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369610/extras/0dd6ed96b7b4d5751207e40885ac9aec.mp4?t=1697834271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
